  "title": "Monsters & Girls",
  "description": "Monsters & Girls adds cute monster girl mobs to Minecraft through a Fabric port of the original Forge mod. It includes Mandrake, Fruit Mandrake, Mushroom, Spook, and Wisp variants for a total of 21 mobs. Players can tame them with cookies and interact.",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oNNgMZk.png\" width=\"1473\" height=\"382\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SIUrjPb.png\" width=\"1155\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DDe1EVK.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"53\" /></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SIUrjPb.png\" width=\"1155\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">📖 <strong>About</strong></span></p>\n<p>Hey guys...<br />New mod and this is quite the cute one at that!</p>\n<p>This is a port I made of the Mod <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/monsters-girls-mushroom-update\">Monsters&amp;Girls</a> made by<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/members/b_art_ek/projects\"> b_art_ek</a>, I'm only porting for fabric since there is no Fabric version, this port is still in it's early stages but I've added quite a few things so you guys can play around with.</p>\n<p>There are 5 types of girls each one of them having several variants with a total of 21 girls! Quite a bit isn't it? Well that's why it took me the time of my life to implement them and there a few yet to implement adding more to that number...</p>\n<p><strong>Quick note!!</strong> Do use <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/roughly-enough-items\">REI </a>mod in order to quick inspect the recipes, while I still haven't added them here!</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SIUrjPb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>📚 Contents</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Mandrake</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uWaHiHf.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"325\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9um8l8m.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"325\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Fruit Mandrake</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d37DfM1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/I9fEoBy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" /><br /><br /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Mushroom</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nLFwclJ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"237\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WDG94tv.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"237\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HUJf5CR.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"237\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iowb7YN.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"237\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/G091lkb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"251\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vNOca94.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"251\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8we563.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"225\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QWnDrUo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"225\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W7hWq5i.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"253\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AzpxrYn.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"251\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oH5bdUY.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"225\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NFERhIU.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"225\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Spook</strong></p>\n<p><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xfOtgjd.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"225\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xM0G6k6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"225\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Wisp</strong><br /><br /></p>\n<p><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XKUJxzb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"253\" /><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4Zb1UHv.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"223\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uEmMsrX.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"253\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SIUrjPb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>✨Interactions</strong></span></p>\n<p><strong>Tame</strong> - For now all the mobs can be tamed using cookies.</p>\n<p><strong>Belly/Tummy</strong> - They can became puffy if they eat apple, if that happen just use a feather and most will be back to normal.</p>\n<p><strong>Sit</strong> - They can sit now! Honestly with all that running around... just left-click with an empty hand.</p>\n<p><strong>Why Everything is Craftable?</strong> - So you can get almost everything in the mod by crafting, even the stem, shroomlight and mushroom blocks for now.</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SIUrjPb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>💡 FAQ</strong></span></p>\n<p><strong>Q: How long will you update this for?</strong><br />A: First they are cute, so I will work on this port from time to time.</p>\n<p><strong><b>Q: There are missing's&nbsp;mobs and features, why don't the spook fly?</b></strong><br />A: Okay okay, got it, I will work on those, with time... trust me...</p>\n<p><strong>Q: What versions will be available, is it just fabric?</strong><br />A: For now I want to update to 1.20 but previous versions I don't now...</p>\n<p><strong>Q: Is it just fabric?</strong><br />A: Only Fabric because the mod is being actively developed, but for forge, that's why I'm porting to Fabric.</p>\n<p><strong>Q: How long will it take for an update to come out?</strong><br />A: I'm thinking on taking a break... so it may take a while.</p>\n<p><strong>Q: Will the mod be the same has its original?</strong><br />A: That's the plan, plus some interesting features :)</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SIUrjPb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>🏆 Credits</strong></span></p>\n<p>Original: <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/monsters-girls-mushroom-update\">Monsters&amp;Girls</a> | <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/members/b_art_ek/projects\">b_art_ek</a></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SIUrjPb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/MSymbios\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q234DB3.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"53\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SIUrjPb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1155\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n\n<p>\n<img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wkKZTdp.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"191\" />\n<img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/M25O2Po.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"191\" />\n</p>",
